<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="20Feb1938"><font color="red">20 February 1938</font> <i>NLPL</i> (to Paul L&eacute;on): The proof will go back in the morning registered &hellip; I don&apos;t know if E.J. can find libretto of  [L??? M???] &hellip; in any case could you copy out of the Opera Book in my flat (among music books, R, lowest shelf near door) the paper about this opera, date etc. Better type it. And let me know the dates of <i>Le Proph&egrave;te</i> (1848?) and <i>L&apos;Africane</i> (62?) </div>
